Disk Sorter Ultimate 9.7.14 - [CrackingPatching] 
Disk Sorter is a good program, the purpose of which is to give you the tools for sorting all the files and directories in the selected area of ​​your hard disk, before that you can set the desired parameters. 
Once launched, you must select a category and the program classifies it. This process is fast enough, although it all depends on how many files and folders in the desired category. Upon completion, you can view all the elements while sorting them by size, extension, creation time, last access time, name and so on. Plus you can organize files by categories, let's say movies in one folder, pictures in another and so on. 
Disk Sorter allows you to view the results in the form of a circular graph or histogram, you can copy data or print them, you can save the report in one of the formats. In general, I liked the program, it works brightly, has many settings, it's a pity there is no Russian language, it would be easier to understand, of course.
